sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor Sender as SenderUser
actor Receiver as ReceiverUser
participant Client as WebClient
participant Socket as SocketService
participant Queue as RabbitMQ
participant Consumer as ChatFriendDmConsumer
participant MsgCtrl as MessageController
participant MsgSvc as MessageService
participant MsgDb as MongoMessage
participant Realtime as RealtimeHub
Sender->>Client: Gui DM/Room message
Client->>Socket: emit friend:send / room:send
Socket->>Queue: publish friend.dm.message
Queue->>Consumer: consume job
Consumer->>MsgCtrl: internal createMessage
MsgCtrl->>MsgSvc: validate payload + business rule
MsgSvc->>MsgDb: save message
alt Save thanh cong
  MsgSvc->>Realtime: publish friend:new_message
  Realtime-->>Receiver: push realtime message
  Realtime-->>Sender: ack sent
else Loi validate/DB
  MsgSvc-->>Socket: error payload
  Socket-->>Sender: emit error
end
Note over MsgSvc,MsgDb: Nhanh bo sung edit/recall/delete/mark-read can authorize chat context
